Package lexparse

Class KnightCodeBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • lexparse.KnightCodeBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    KnightCodeListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    public class KnightCodeBaseListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements KnightCodeListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of KnightCodeListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
